> ; ******************************************************************************
> ; *                                                                            *
> ; *                  TEST NATURAL VS ARTIFICIAL LIGHTSOURCES                   *
> ; *                                                                            *
> ; *                      VERBS AFFECTING LIT/UNLIT STATUS                      *
> ; *                                                                            *
> ; ******************************************************************************
> ; Ensure that only the correct verbs can be used with natural and artificial
> ; light sources.
> ; ==============================================================================
> ; NATURAL LIGHT SOURCE: CANDLE
> ; ==============================================================================
> ; ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
> ; ALLOWED VERBS
> ; ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
> ; The following verbs can be used with natural light sources:
> ; VERB `extinguish`
> extinguish candle
But the candle is not lit.

> put out candle
But the candle is not lit.

> put candle out
But the candle is not lit.

> ; VERB `light`
> light candle
You light the candle.

> ; ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
> ; ILLEGAL VERBS
> ; ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
> ; The following verbs can not be used with natural light sources:
> ; VERB `turn_on`
> turn on candle
That's not something you can turn on.

> switch on candle
That's not something you can switch on.

> ; VERB `turn_off`
> switch off candle
That's not something you can switch off.

> turn off candle
That's not something you can turn off.

> ; ==============================================================================
> ; ARTIFICIAL LIGHT SOURCE: FLASHLIGHT
> ; ==============================================================================
> ; ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
> ; ALLOWED VERBS
> ; ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
> ; The following verbs can be used with artificial light sources:
> ; VERB `light`
> light flashlight
You turn on the flashlight.

> ; VERB `switch`
> switch flashlight
You switch off the flashlight.

> switch flashlight
You switch on the flashlight.

> ; VERB `turn_on`
> turn on flashlight
The flashlight is already lit.

> turn flashlight on
The flashlight is already lit.

> switch on flashlight
The flashlight is already lit.

> switch flashlight on
The flashlight is already lit.

> ; VERB `turn_off`
> turn off flashlight
You turn off the flashlight.

> turn flashlight off
But the flashlight is not lit.

> switch off flashlight
But the flashlight is not lit.

> switch flashlight off
But the flashlight is not lit.

